{
  "id": "adv_bond_kor_01_05",
  "title": "fran5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁ、疲れたわ～。こんな夜遅くなるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ I'm exhausted~. I can't believe it got this late…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あのプロデューサー、次会ったらどうしてやろうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That producer… I'll show him what's what next time we meet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 10.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "もうタクシーに乗って帰りたいくらいだけど……\nこの間勧められた、成長株買ったばかりだしね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd love to just grab a taxi and head home‚ but…\nI just bought those growth stocks I was recommended lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、お疲れ様です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san‚ good work today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 166.66666660000118
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.999995931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ひゃあっ！　……って、雫か……突然話しかけないでよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek! … Oh‚ it's just you‚ Shizuku. Don't scare me like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.999995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "雫もこの近くで仕事だったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you working nearby too‚ Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まぁ、そんなところです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ something like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.9333292644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……雑誌の撮影、随分遅くなったんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The magazine shoot ran quite late‚ didn't it?…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.4649164518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "え、えぇ……思ったよりいい写真が撮れたから\n他にもポーズを試したいって言われてこんな時間に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah… they said they got better shots than expected‚\nso they wanted to try more poses‚ and it ended up this late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4649164518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.7649164518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、時間外労働もいいところね\nま、私の美貌だし仕方ないけれど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ talk about excessive overtime.\nWell‚ I suppose it can't be helped given my beauty.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7649164518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さすがは、franさん……この前のグラビア撮影でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of fran-san… Even at that last photoshoot‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6315831185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 54.6315831185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "追加で二着も水着を試してましたよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you tried on two extra swimsuits‚ didn't you?…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうね……って、あら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right… Wait‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6736917179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.6736917179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "まだそのグラビアは世に出てないはずだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That spread shouldn't be out in the world yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.4736917179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……franさんの水着、楽しみ……\n鑑賞用と保存用と布教用に五冊は買います……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… I'm looking forward to seeing you in a swimsuit…\nI'll buy five copies—for viewing‚ for keeping‚ and for spreading the word…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4736917179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そ、そう……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8378866514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.8378866514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "じゃ、私はもう帰るから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I'm heading home now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.6712199848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "待って、franさん……これ、差し入れです\n良かったら食べて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ fran-san… here‚ this is for you.\nPlease have some if you'd like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6712199848,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2895.4466818999977
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これ、賑飯庵のロケ弁？　しかも人気のすき焼き弁当",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this a catering box from 'Nigimeshian'? And it's the popular sukiyaki one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6246893247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.6246893247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "じゃない！　こんないいお弁当、どうしたのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way! How did you get such a fancy meal box?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "franさん、いつも仕事で余ったお弁当沢山持って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san‚ you're always taking home lots of leftover meals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2580175718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 99.2580175718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "帰ってるから、私の分のお弁当も渡そうと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "from work‚ so I wanted to give you mine too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日もハンバーグと焼き魚弁当を五つ……お水三本に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today you took five hamburger and grilled fish sets… three bottles of water‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5125075341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 108.5125075341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "割り箸も沢山持って帰ってますよね……総額7300円",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and plenty of disposable chopsticks too… Total value: 7‚300 yen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.5382901828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "え……！？　……ど、どうして雫がそんなこと\n知ってるのよ！？　しかもいやらしく値段まで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What…!? …H-How do you know all that‚\nShizuku!? And why do you know the exact price?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5382901828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "へへへ……franさんのことならなんでも知ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… I know everything about fran-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2049568494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.2049568494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_05-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "トップオタとして、当たり前……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As your top fan‚ it's only natural…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
